---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { User, Heart, Sparkles, Flower2, Sun, Wind, Activity } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout title="Maya Patel - Wellness Coach & Writer | RealMindSolutions" description="Maya Patel is a wellness coach and writer focused on holistic mental health, mindfulness, self-care, and integrative approaches to well-being.">
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-brand-primary-50/30 to-white pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
        {/* Author Avatar */}
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-100 to-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <User class="w-20 h-20 md:w-24 md:h-24 text-orange-600" />
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Author Info */}
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Maya Patel</h1>
          <p class="font-serif italic text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-600 mb-6">Wellness Coach & Writer</p>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Maya Patel is a certified wellness coach and writer specializing in holistic mental health, mindfulness practices, and sustainable self-care. With training in both traditional mental health approaches and complementary wellness modalities, Maya helps people create personalized well-being practices that fit their lives.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Her writing emphasizes the connection between mind, body, and spirit—exploring how nutrition, movement, sleep, mindfulness, and social connection all contribute to mental health. Maya believes wellness isn't one-size-fits-all, and encourages readers to experiment and find what works for them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Expertise & Writing Topics */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Areas of Expertise</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Flower2 class="h-6 w-6 text-orange-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-900">Mindfulness & Meditation</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-orange-800">
            Practical guidance on mindfulness meditation, breathwork, body awareness, and present-moment practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Heart class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900">Self-Care & Boundaries</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">
            Building sustainable self-care routines, setting boundaries, and avoiding burnout in demanding lives.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Activity class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-900">Mind-Body Connection</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-800">
            How physical health affects mental health—nutrition, exercise, sleep, and somatic practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Sun class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-900">Holistic Mental Health</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-purple-800">
            Integrative approaches combining therapy with wellness practices like yoga, nutrition, and nature connection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Wind class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-900">Stress Management</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-indigo-800">
            Practical techniques for managing stress, anxiety, and overwhelm through lifestyle and mindfulness tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-pink-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Sparkles class="h-6 w-6 text-pink-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-pink-900">Personal Growth</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-pink-800">
            Self-discovery, values clarification, goal-setting, and cultivating resilience and purpose.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Background & Credentials */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Background & Experience</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Professional Experience</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-0">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">7+ years</strong> as a wellness coach working with individuals on holistic health and well-being
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Writing experience</strong> - Mental health wellness publications, mindfulness platforms, and lifestyle websites
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Workshop facilitator</strong> - Mindfulness meditation, stress management, and self-care workshops
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Collaborated with</strong> therapists, nutritionists, and yoga instructors for integrated care
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Corporate wellness</strong> - Employee well-being programs and stress reduction training
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Education & Certifications</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-0">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Certified Wellness Coach</strong> - National Board for Health & Wellness Coaching
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Mindfulness-Based Stress Reduction</strong> - MBSR Teacher Training (Palouse Mindfulness)
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">200-Hour Yoga Teacher Training</strong> - Certified yoga instructor
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">B.A. in Psychology</strong> - Minor in Nutrition Science
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Additional training</strong> - Somatic practices, health coaching, motivational interviewing
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Writing Philosophy */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Writing Philosophy</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl">
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-brand-primary bg-gray-50 p-6 italic text-lg text-gray-800">
          "Mental health isn't just about therapy—it's about how we eat, move, sleep, breathe, connect, and care for ourselves daily. My writing explores the full spectrum of well-being, honoring both clinical treatment and the everyday practices that support our mental health."
        </blockquote>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 not-prose">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-900 mb-3">Core Values:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-orange-800">
            <li>• <strong>Holistic perspective:</strong> Viewing mental health through the lens of whole-person wellness</li>
            <li>• <strong>Accessibility:</strong> Offering low-cost and free wellness practices alongside professional treatment</li>
            <li>• <strong>Individualization:</strong> Recognizing that wellness looks different for everyone—no judgment or prescriptions</li>
            <li>• <strong>Integration:</strong> Showing how therapy and wellness practices can work together synergistically</li>
            <li>• <strong>Sustainability:</strong> Focusing on realistic, long-term practices rather than quick fixes or perfection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Articles Coming Soon */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Articles by Maya Patel</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Maya's articles are currently in development. Upcoming pieces will cover:
        </p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• 10-minute mindfulness practices for anxious minds</li>
          <li>• How to build a self-care routine that actually sticks</li>
          <li>• The connection between gut health and anxiety</li>
          <li>• Yoga for mental health: What the research shows</li>
          <li>• Setting boundaries without feeling selfish</li>
          <li>• Sleep hygiene for depression: Small changes, big impact</li>
          <li>• Breathwork techniques therapists recommend</li>
          <li>• Combining therapy with wellness practices: A holistic approach</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          In the meantime, explore related topics below.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Related Topics */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Topics Maya Covers</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/tag/mindfulness" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Mindfulness</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/self-care" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Self-Care</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/anxiety" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Anxiety</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/depression" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Depression</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapy" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapy</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/mental-health" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Mental Health</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
